re-root MR is always established for graphene with charged impurities in a\ngeneric gated setup at low temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Oct 2012 22:50:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 Mar 2013 10:36:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-11"}
