) GeV in the 2delanQCD model, which,\nhowever, are compatible with recent lattice calculations. In perturbative QCD\nin MSbar scheme these effects are even stronger and give larger uncertainties\nin mbbar. The (F)APT model gives small ultrasoft effects and the extracted\nvalues of mbbar agree with those in most of the literature: mbbar(mbbar)\n=approx 4.2 GeV. The extracted values of mcbar(mcbar) in all four models are\nabout 1.26-1.27 GeV and agree well with those in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Oct 2012 03:35:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Mar 2013 14:35:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-12"}
