y solving a full set of linearized equations. The effective\nsound speed generalizes the Toomre stability parameter of the Jeans mode to\nallow for the mixed GI of vertically-stratified, pressure-confined disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Oct 2012 11:46:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
